articles.title: SHIF Phase 2 rollout faces implementation challenges
articles.description: SHIF Phase 2 rollout faces implementation challenges. SHIF Phase 2 Implementation continues to dominate Kenyan policy discourse as stakeholders weigh in on the implications for ordinary citizens.
articles.content: SHIF Phase 2 rollout faces implementation challenges. The SHIF Phase 2 Implementation has been a subject of intense debate across Kenya. Analysts say the policy will have significant implications for the health sector. Various stakeholders including civil society groups, business associations, and county governments have expressed diverse opinions on the matter.
